  "subject": "Don't use keytool in junits",
  "commit_message": "Don't use keytool in junits\n\nModified SelfSignedKeyStore to use a pre-created keystore file\ninstead of using keytool.\n\nThe keystore file contains a key that is good for 10 years.  It was\ngenerated using docker/csit/gen_keystore.sh, after changing \"30\" to\n\"3650\" through-out the script.\n\nIssue-ID: POLICY-3587\nChange-Id: I58f02aa942dd2af74795e25db0a3487d32508f70\nSigned-off-by: Jim Hahn <jrh3.lf@gmail.com>\n",
