        "timestamp": "2021-09-21 15:19:20.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 3: Code-Review+1\n\nThis is an alternative to the other review, taking the approach of using a pre-created keystore, thus avoiding the need for keytool or bouncycastle.\n\nNote: this keystore is good for 10 years.  A 10-year key might generate a security exception, but this keystore is not included in production code.  Nevertheless, can always regenerate it with just a one year, if desired - simply run gen_truststore.sh & gen_keystore.sh, after modifying the validity period in gen_keystore.sh from 30 days to 365 days.",
        "patchset_number": 3
      },
